attributes.title: Surviving Santa's Naughty List - White Noise 2
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay! In this White Noise 2 gameplay, teamwork is key, unless the monster is Santa, then you're just f**ked...

attributes.title: Now THIS Is Impossible - We Need to Go Deeper
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay! The gang revisits We Need to Go Deeper with first timer Alfredo and oh boy has it changed!

attributes.title: Sharks VS Divers - Depth
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay! The gang dives in to Depth. It's Sharks VS Divers in this depth-defying gameplay

attributes.title: There's Been a BETRAYAL! - Halo Reach Multiplayer
attributes.description: We're playing some Halo Reach Multiplayer and there's going to be some betrayal.

attributes.title: There's A Lot of Blood in That Lamp - Gmod: Prop Hunt
attributes.description: Those rapscallions are having themselves a high noon duel in a rickety wild west town, prop hunt style. Love, betrayal, bieszczady, this episode has it all!

attributes.title: We Give Alfredo a Controller - Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Remastered
attributes.description: Can the boys go toe to toe against Mister Diamond himself if he has to use a controller while they're on mice?

attributes.title: Dicks Out for RouLetsPlay
attributes.description: The gang introduces Fiona to Genital Jousting in this RouLetsPlay!

attributes.title: Our Arrows Don't Fly Straight - Towerfall
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and it's time for some Towerfall. Let's see who can survive the longest and who's the luckiest with aiming all those arrows.

attributes.title: This Isn't Tomb Raider - Ultimate Chicken Horse
attributes.description: You may be wondering why this isn't Tomb Raider. Well, long story short, Sarah said to film something, and Tomb Raider wasn't working. So we asked, do we need more Ultimate Chicken Horse? Of course we do.

attributes.title: Tomb Raider: Definitive Edition - Red Barrels in Fact Explode
attributes.description: It's finally time for the actual Tomb Raider Rouletsplay. Let's blow up some barrels in this multiplayer gameplay!

attributes.title: Gotta Go Fast! - SpeedRunners
attributes.description: It's Rouletsplay and it's time for some classic racing in some SpeedRunners gameplay!

attributes.title: We Make the Ender Dragon FLY in Gmod TTT
attributes.description: It's Rouletsplay with some TTT in Gmod! Jack learns to fly and Jeremy goes on a killing spree.

attributes.title: This Isn't Even Fair - Trials Evolution
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay! Chad joins us and gets to experience Jack's wrath that he delivers in Trials Evolution!

attributes.title: MORE Sharks - Depth
attributes.description: Sharks VS Divers in this depth defying RouLetsPlay!

attributes.title: Golf It - There Is a Murderer on the Floating Islands
attributes.description: It's Rouletsplay and it's Golf It time! How many bips does it take to push someone over the edge?

attributes.title: Trivia Murder Party 2 - With a Killer Voice
attributes.description: RouLetsPlay is back with Trivia Murder Party 2 and Jeremy's killer voice is back at it again.

attributes.title: Taze Them in the Tit - The Blackout Club
attributes.description: It's Rouletsplay and time for The Blackout Club. It's only been a year since we've touched this one, what could possibly go wrong?

attributes.title: The Wreckoning - Wreckfest
attributes.description: It's Rouletsplay, but more importantly, it's time to get wrecked! It's a vehicular battle for the ages in Wreckfest.

attributes.title: Infinite Falling Limbs - Viscera Cleanup Detail
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and it's time to deep clean in this speed round addition of Viscera Cleanup Detail.

attributes.title: Grenades Go Boom Boom -  Hand Simulator
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and Hand Simulator. Lets see how many grenades we can have explode at once!

attributes.title: Battle of the Gents - Gang Beasts
attributes.description: It's time for RouLetsPlay and some more Gang Beasts! In this video, Ryan and Jack really have it out for each other.

attributes.title: Weaponizing Chickens  - Witch It
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and a spin on hide and seek called Witch It!

attributes.title: SOLO and a Guy: A Star Wars Story - Battlefront II
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and we're playing Battlefront 2! It's time to 'pew pew' and run away from Vader himself!

attributes.title: Power-ups Change Everything! - Rocket League
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and Rocket League! Power-ups in this game sure can increase your skill level!

attributes.title: Aiming With Controllers is HARD! - Call of Duty Black Ops
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for GUN GAME in some classic Call of Duty Black Ops on Xbox 360.

attributes.title: Making The World BURN - Worms W.M.D.
attributes.description: It's time for some more RouLetsPlay and Worms W.M.D.!  Send in the airdrops!

attributes.title: TWO SPINS!?! - Goldeneye: Source and Half Dead 2
attributes.description: We're back with Rouletsplay! This time it's a double-feature!

attributes.title: Lindsay Outranks Everyone - Rainbow Six Vegas 2
attributes.description: It's time for some classic Rainbow Six Vegas 2! Surely no one would team kill in this RouLetsPlay...

attributes.title: Drawing Ourselves in Drawful 2
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay time again! We're back at it in Drawful 2, learning about the Motzart Diet and Pope Grubhub.

attributes.title: Too Many Chiefs - Halo 3
attributes.description: RooooooooooooouLetsPlay! We're seeing double in Halo MCC: Halo 3.

attributes.title: Too Many Chefs - Overcooked 2!
attributes.description: We're back with RouLetsPlay! We're making everyone's favorite camping food! ....pizza?

attributes.title: Grappling Each Other to Death - SpeedRunners
attributes.description: It's Rouletsplay and Speedrunners. That's right NOT Starwhal. I mean we wanted to but the technology Gods said NO! Anyway, Let's grapple hook each other to death!

attributes.title: You Had Me at Deathmatch - Doom Multiplayer
attributes.description: The gang learns the power of teamwork, the value of treachery, and the true meaning of friendship - all while trying to avoid prematuraly falling to their deaths.

attributes.title: Jumpin' and Bumpin' in the Basement - Hot Lava
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and we jump into some Hot Lava in the basement levels. This certainly becomes a challenge for some of us.

attributes.title: This Is STILL a Game? - Totally Accurate Battlegrounds
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for some Totally Accurate Battlegrounds. Oh! You can also actually aim now!

attributes.title: Weapon Modding is STRONG! - Dying Light: Bad Blood
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for some Dying Light: Bad Blood! I know I know, it's not Battlefront 2. I'm sure we'll get there someday though!

attributes.title: Who Are The Bug Men of St. Christopher? - Fibbage 3
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for a wild game of Fibbage 3. Feast your eyes on a rare picture of the past, the Bug Men of St. Christopher.

attributes.title: The Many Perspectives of Golf - Golf With Your Friends
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for some bippin'! Who will win this time?

attributes.title: A Terrifying Seduction - White Noise 2
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and let's play a little White Noise 2. Lilith, the Goddess of night, is here to steal your heart!

attributes.title: Toothpaste is So Sticky
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for some Gang Beasts. Some of you think the wheel is rigged. As the editor, I'd like to share it's truly a magical wheel. My mind is blown every time they spin it.

attributes.title: Pew Pew les Zombies
attributes.description: It's RouletsPlay and time for some Killing Floor 2. Fiona bonds with her French character and Alfredo tries to make pumpkin bread.

attributes.title: The Boy Who Lived
attributes.description: It's RouletsPlay and time for some Stick Fight. Snakes, shoots, and splatters.

attributes.title: One of Us is Synthetic - Moving Out
attributes.description: The almighty spin told us to play Moving Out. Four of us are here, but only three of us are real. Which one's the fake?

attributes.title: Who's That Nancy Wheeler? - Dead By Daylight
attributes.description: We discover a brand-new Pokemon in this horrifying and hilarious round of Dead By Daylight. It's Nancy Wheeler!!

attributes.title: Shotguns are MEAN! - Payday 2
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time to test our skills in some Payday 2. Mask up friends.

attributes.title: It's Not Fair Playing Alfredo - Counter-Strike: Global Offensive
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and the Achievement Hunter gang gets to experience what our pal Alfredo is really capable of with one of his old favorites, Counter-Strike GLobal Offensive.

attributes.title: Leave My Eggs Alone! - White Noise 2
attributes.description: Jeremy hunts the hunters in this horror monster mash.

attributes.title: We Light Ourselves on Fire! - Left 4 Dead 2
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay and time for some Left 4 Dead 2. How Hard could it possibly be to survive while waiting for a helicopter and being mauled by zombies? Maybe some Malatov Cocktails will help?

attributes.title: Shut the F* up! - In Silence
attributes.description: It's RouLetsPlay again and it's time for something new. Let's test out the proximity chat in In Silence. I'm sure the technology Gods will be on our side...

attributes.title: Santas Space Team - Deep Rock Galactic
attributes.description: Its RouLetsPlay again and we dive back into Deep Rock Galactic! Between discovering space presents to getting covered in goo, lets see if we can survive this exploration.
